{"tid":425260,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"(暗瘡A酸) 召喚所有食過／食緊／想食a酸既巴絲","createTime":"2017-10-05T14:36:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T15:05:26.000Z","uid":55475,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"ba6106ccbe6ad36546cde7dfc1762b6995daa5e2","tid":425260,"uid":55475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:36:39.000Z","msg":"爛面真係好難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日係街望到人地塊面白白滑滑<br />\n自己就成堆暗瘡 白頭粉刺<br />\n成面都係閉合性粉刺<br />\n好難頂 朋友問起真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbook左下星期睇皮膚科 mk dr.chan <br />\n想食a酸 爬左一陣文 想問定各位巴絲 <br />\n原廠定係O牌分別大唔大？<br />\n你地價錢貴唔貴？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n爆發期爆左幾耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲食A酸成功清到D閉合性粉刺 即係D暗粒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"234b5fbc0e425b5ab4985c57f657d66d9eef160a","tid":425260,"uid":55475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:41:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"389141782347215cab1cb20c1d6344c57997027d","tid":425260,"uid":32542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:47:29.000Z","msg":"食緊第4盒都仲有瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56c59f765b0b9992ac54afe0a81194ebe89d4c1f","tid":425260,"uid":6532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:00:37.000Z","msg":"食左兩次療程2011一次，2014第二次，好返九成，而家簡唔中爆一兩粒。<br />\n第一次食o字頭，第二次食泰爾絲，平o字同幾倍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8a4a1c9514a1eace2fc674048eab260bb69c045","tid":425260,"uid":140438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T15:14:42.000Z","ms